( ( ( power K ) . (L,( deg MT )) ) * ( b1 /. S ) ) = ( ( MT |^ ( deg MT ) ) . ( b1 /. S ) ) by A1,A3,CKB48:1
.= ( ( ZeroMap (V1,V1) ) . ( b1 /. S ) ) by CKB35:def 1
.= ( ( (the carrier of V1) --> ( 0. V1 ) ) . ( b1 /. S ) ) by GRCAT_1:def 7
